    {
      "id": "23b7433e_a6d38bd1",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/aaf/components/aaf-cert-service/values.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 91,
      "message": "ahh. By convention we call sth XXXExternalSecret when this field holds the name of external secret to be used and when this evaluates to true (using tpl) then we consider that external secret is used.\n\nIf it's not the case then where do you set the name of external secret that should be used?",
